titleInfo.subTitle: JUDGMENT AND DECREE OF FORECLOSURE AND ORDER OF SALE- Plaintiff's Motion for Default Judgment 8 is granted; Judgment is entered against defendants Albert L. titleInfo.title: United States of America v. Zook et al
titleInfo.subTitle: ORDER that by 12/29/05, any person claiming an interest in the proceeds from the sale of the property that is the subject of this action shall file a Notice of claim with this Court. Copies mailed to Albert Zook and Collection Associates.(JSF)
